# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Use English only. Keep the subject imperative, present tense, and under 72 characters.
#
# Types:
# feat:     New user-facing functionality
# fix:      Bug fix
# docs:     Documentation only
# test:     Tests only
# refactor: Code change without behavior change
# chore:    Tooling, build, dependency, or maintenance work
# ci:       Continuous integration changes
#
# Example:
# feat(cli): add localized insight report command
#
# Body:
# Explain what changed and why. Wrap at 72 characters.
#
# Footer:
# Reference issues or breaking changes when needed.
